<li id="cite_note-HTS-2000-7"><b><a href="#cite_ref-HTS-2000_7-0" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.aluminumrepair.com/more_info.asp" class="external text" title="http://www.aluminumrepair.com/more_info.asp" rel="nofollow">HTS-2000</a>, accessed 2009-03-09</li>
<li id="cite_note-8"><b><a href="#cite_ref-8" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.toolingu.com/definition-660130-28677-soldering-torch.html" class="external text" title="http://www.toolingu.com/definition-660130-28677-soldering-torch.html" rel="nofollow">What is the definition of soldering torch?</a></li>
</ol>
